Class SimpleTable

  • java.lang.Object
    • markdown_excel.table.SimpleTable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Table
    public class SimpleTable
extends Object
implements Table
    A simple implementation of Table, backed by nested ArrayList's which are used in a row-major fashion.
